IN
VITRO
SUSCEPTIBILITY
OF
PSEUDOMONAS
TO
FOUR
BETALACTAMANTIBIOTICS
AMPICILLIN
CEPHALOTHIN
CARBENICILLIN
PIPERACILLIN
TO
FOUR
AMINOGLYCOSIDES
KANAMYCIN
AMIKACIN
GENTAMICIN
TOBRAMYCIN
AND
TO
